sowingBar[{{x0_, x1_}, {y0_, y1_}}, __] := (Sow[{x1 - x0, 100*(y1 - y0)}]; Rectangle[{x0, y0}, {x1, y1}]) {histogram, newdata} = Reap[Histogram[data, Automatic, "Probability", ChartElementFunction -> sowingBar]]; histogram Create a polar histogram of the wind-direction frequencies:
